title: Are the Cowboys vulnerable?
itunes:title: Are the Cowboys vulnerable?
description:
A room filled with heroes – Dan Hanzus, Marc Sessler, Chris Wesseling, & Gregg Rosenthal – recap all the latest news from around the NFL including the Cowboys cutting Lucky Whitehead and extending La'el Collins. Marc then reads his ode to the newest possible Browns superstar before the heroes recap the second season of "All or Nothing."
